<p>Need to set a class to the generated <code>$flyout</code> image before display. Currently API has only <code>onShow</code>, <code>onMove</code> &amp; <code>onHide</code> options.</p>  <p>Although this adds the class, I need it to be added before the <code>onShow</code> event.</p>  <pre><code>var $easyzoom = $('.easyzoom').easyZoom({     onShow: function() {         $('img', this.$flyout).addClass('zoomed');     } }); </code></pre>  <p><a href="http://i-like-robots.github.io/EasyZoom/" rel="nofollow">http://i-like-robots.github.io/EasyZoom/</a></p>